This is a simple sinatra app. It is a place to try out features of simple web applications (and to
demonstrate some interesting things--at least in my opinion--about sinatra. There isn't a lot here yet,
but I will be adding more.

Note that I habe tried to commet as much as possible.

The project has empty log and db folders. When you first run the app a db and two logs are created in the
appropriate directories.
